* ============================================================
* HLASM PROGRAM WITH MACRO CALLS
* Tests: macro expansion via copybooks, parameter substitution
* ============================================================
MACROPROG CSECT
         BALR  12,0
         USING *,12
*
* Use SAVEREGS macro to save registers
         SAVEREGS MYSAVE
*
* Use PRINTMSG macro to print a greeting
         PRINTMSG GREETING,13
*
* Return
         L     13,MYSAVE+4
         LM    14,12,12(13)
         BR    14
*
MYSAVE   DC    18F'0'
GREETING DC    C'HELLO WORLD!'
*
         END   MACROPROG
